e17013f3-d4a1-436e-af6e-bdd8d62bfdfb	b9360b14-c470-4970-81d3-6b7761eb5b1a	What is clustering in machine learning?	Clustering is the process of grouping similar data points together to identify structures within data. It is an unsupervised learning technique, meaning it does not rely on predefined labels.	0	EASY	Clustering Basics	2025-11-03 07:54:34.645332	2025-11-03 07:54:34.645332
