305985bb-4613-4a46-8a6b-7aa21b0f5c58	36b47c7d-51d4-43f9-974f-756d567748e4	3	rns from examples of spam and non-spam emails, improving its performance over time.\n\n**1.2 Types of Machine Learning**\n\nMachine learning is categorized into several types based on the nature of the learning task:\n\n- **Supervised Learning**: Here, the model is trained on a labeled dataset. Imagine teaching a child to distinguish cats from dogs by showing them pictures labeled as either cat or dog.\n  \n- **Unsupervised Learning**: In this scenario, the model is given data without explicit instructions on what to do with it. Think of this as giving a group of people a collection of photos and asking them to sort them into meaningful categories without telling them what those categories might be.\n\n- **Reinforcement Learning**: This is akin to training a dog where actions are rewarded or punished. The model learns to make decisions by receiving feedback from its actions.\n\n**Ask yourself:** How do these types of learning apply to real-world problems you're interested in solving?\n\n**1.	CONTENT	248	{"start_pos": 2366, "end_pos": 3358, "length": 992}	2025-11-27 12:30:55.557855	2025-11-27 12:30:55.557858
